dcterms:description: A dataset containing comparisons for the attributes of diverse behaviors, collected through crowdsourcing to quantify human preferences.
dcterms:title: Multi-Perspective Human Feedback Datasets

dcterms:description: A dataset used for training and evaluating locomotion tasks involving a single-legged robot, focusing on speed and jump height attributes.
dcterms:title: Hopper Dataset

dcterms:description: A dataset used for training and evaluating locomotion tasks involving a bipedal robot, focusing on speed, torso height, stride length, left-right leg preference, and humanness attributes.
dcterms:title: Walker Dataset

dcterms:description: A dataset used for training and evaluating locomotion tasks involving a humanoid robot, focusing on speed, head height, and humanness attributes.
dcterms:title: Humanoid Dataset
